\subsection{Method \code{close_short()}}{
Close a Short Position (Buy Back and Repay)

Buys back the base asset and automatically repays the loan. This
closes a short position opened with \code{open_short()}.

\strong{What happens under the hood:}
\enumerate{
\item KuCoin buys the base asset (e.g. BTC) on the market.
\item The purchased asset is automatically used to repay your loan.
\item If the price dropped since you opened the short, you profit.
}
\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{POST https://api.kucoin.com/api/v3/hf/margin/order}
}

